<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Restat</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .credentials {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .credentials p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #999;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://github.com/umar-phaedra/assets/blob/main/logo-icon-restat.png?raw=true" alt="" />
            <h1>Welcome, {{name}}!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Thank you for using our service.</p>
            <p>Your OTP (One-Time Password) for verifying your account is:</p>
            <b>{{otp}}</b>
            <p>This code is valid for the next <b>[{{expirationTime}} minutes]</b> and can be used only once. Please enter this code in the verification field to complete your registration or login process.</p>
            <p>If you did not request this code, please ignore this email. For any concerns, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>The Restat Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; {{currentYear}} Restat. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
